text.tspan: Lastly, the investigation of network forensics techniques, including as sniffing and rule-based
extraction, has offered new paths for identifying suspects and their interactions on WhatsApp.
By focusing on IP address identification and network traffic analysis, these studies give law
enforcement with additional methods to track and intercept illegal actions done over encrypted
messaging platforms (Waqas Ahmed; Faisal Shahzad & L. Ali, 2021).
